NAME

  Hebrew - Source code filter to escape Hebrew script

SYNOPSIS

  use Hebrew;

DESCRIPTION

  The Hebrew software provides character oriented Perl scripting
  environment in Hebrew by easy installation and easy usage.

  - Character oriented regular expression
  - Character oriented run-time routines
  - Character oriented subroutines
      and
  - Byte oriented CORE::* functions
  - Byte oriented regular expression on /b modifier

  Information processing model beginning with perl3 or this software.

    +--------------------------------------------+
    |       Text strings as Binary strings       |
    |       Binary strings as Text strings       |
    +--------------------------------------------+
    |              Not UTF8 Flagged              |
    +--------------------------------------------+

INSTALLATION

  Just copy Hebrew.pm and Ehebrew.pm to your @INC directory.
  For example, to C:\Perl\site\lib

SUBROUTINES

  Hebrew::length(charstring)
  Hebrew::substr(charstring, charpos, charlen)
  etc

SEE ALSO

  http://search.cpan.org/~ina/

